</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="49.[151,1436,656,972]" box="[199,649,944,972]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,386,944,971]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Activity period.</emphasis>
